don't loan out anything to people&quot;. It was then when I realized that I have
absolutely no connection to these people. We have nothing in common. What the hell
was I doing showing up to the hospital to show my support.
<p>
 They talk a lot about
giving back what was given but the truth is that the well only pumps one way with
these people. I've never gotten an amends from anyone in the program, despite their
