<p>
A lot of these AA dickheads spend so
much time in meetings that they don't really know much of anything else. They kind
of lose touch with reality.  AAer's talk about anger being a liability but to me?
Its one of god's greatest gifts, it gets a lot done. AAer's know only one world and
